<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="film-n">film <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fɪlm/    美 /fɪlm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-ame-movie">1.★ <strong>[C] 影片；电影 (AmE movie)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>silent film</strong> 
无声电影</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>watch</strong> / <strong>see a film</strong>
看电影</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>an action</strong> / <strong>a war film</strong>
动作/战争片</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>make / shoot a film</strong>
拍电影</p></div>

<h4 id="2c-u">2.<strong>[C] &amp; [U] 胶卷；胶片：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a roll of colour film
一卷彩色胶卷</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The whole incident was recorded / captured <strong>on film</strong>.
事件的整个过程都被拍摄了下来。</p></div></div>